{"tid":1601912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"‘’時代革命‘’個個都識嗌，但你做既野配唔配得上呢句野","createTime":"2019-09-29T08:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T09:08:00.000Z","uid":224007,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32a43bd1949457e469bf90c8997453e101112a02","tid":1601912,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:30:18.000Z","msg":"口號唔係淨係嗌，係要去實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n變身火魔法師你又要屌<br />\n鶳你又要屌<br />\n黨鐵閘你又唔夠膽跳<br />\n罷工又唔做<br />\n塞路又屌阻到人返工<br />\n文宣又無人做<br />\n行動post又無人推<br />\n<br />\n革乜撚野命呀仲？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請用行動表示你既意志</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做唔到前線都可以做文宣既啫 罷撘黨鐵做到啦呱 罷食藍底食肆都做得到呱<br />\n仲有想贏既今日就同我出黎 話比班popo知我地係唔會驚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請用最大既努力去打呢場扙 一輸我地無架啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"51f2a15fd094f73cdffd450a95cbe16bef21adea","tid":1601912,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"嗌返句啱既口號先得唔得<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得今日為咩出黎<br />\n<br />\n叫少一日黑警得唔得<br />\n<br />\n跟我叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Fight For Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong is Not China<br />\n<br />\nAgainst CCP, the world stands with me.</span></span>"},{"pid":"65faabd42a1c6febae3fbee8a657f3fd868bfe59","tid":1601912,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7832af0685ec61d800dcc63b70e6fd17fa93cf3f","tid":1601912,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd342181139928b7e586b38d0764fb8531ab218","tid":1601912,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"手足們做既野<br />\n 不完美 需改善 但可接受<b